{"tid":2127167,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"遭陳志全私人檢控　郭偉強申請押後至選舉後(9月14日)答辯","createTime":"2020-07-27T07:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T08:04:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5a02f270d32b3e59d258f0ca48aabe9752245704","tid":2127167,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"立法會議員陳志全就5月初發生的內務委員會衝突，提出私人檢控議員郭偉強普通襲擊，於上月獲司法機構批准。郭偉強今午（27日）就本宗傳票案到西九龍法院應訊，他暫時毋須答辯。辯方申請押後，指需時研究文件及待律政司考慮會否介入，並指因立法會選舉臨近，被告不欲本案成為政治炒作，故要求押後案件至選舉完結。裁判官遂把案押至9月14日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，有人提出告發，指稱被告郭偉強於2020年5月8日於香港中環立法會道1號立法會綜合大樓1號會議室，有意或罔顧後果地，致使陳志全意識到即時和不合法的人身暴力，因而襲擊陳志全。<br />\n<br />\n據相關報道，內會於5月8日會議期間爆發主席選舉風波，陳志全指在衝突間遭郭偉強拉跌，並在地上短暫拖行。<br />\n<br />\n今午郭進入法院時，情況一度混亂，一名青少沿途阻撓郭前行，並向他舉中指指罵。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 東網"},{"pid":"c5b1a5cc6202bced406a6e572d77694399e5d453","tid":2127167,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb771b7476345d11af304afa5e6250517eb9901","tid":2127167,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b1a5cc6202bced406a6e572d77694399e5d453","tid":2127167,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f5d9030363bd48291483ae936b555ae98f29b5","tid":2127167,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}